{"tid":1768061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我愛港女：12.8 民陣已獲發大遊行","createTime":"2019-12-03T20:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T10:21:54.000Z","uid":161701,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"40a8b83581486b1e2fa83213d45ea19aae555cd8","tid":1768061,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:28:51.000Z","msg":"12.8 前<br />\n求求求一眾和理非<br />\n唔好諗住自己出就得唔同朋友講<br />\n記住記住記住<br />\n有d人真係百屌先能佢才<br />\n你唔叫佢係唔會郁<br />\n<br />\n第二樣<br />\n文宣組可唔可以派返傳單<br />\n我知你地驚俾白衫斬俾黑警屈<br />\n但可唔可以唔好屈服<br />\n盡量邊派邊走<br />\n搵幾隻哨喺大馬路睇住<br />\n總之有狗就走<br />\n應承我！<br />\n安全至上<br />\n但唔代表可以口停手停<br />\n<br />\n第三樣<br />\n前線避免陣地戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四樣<br />\n唔好再集中一地長時間撚狗<br />\n撚狗和理非請你返自己嗰區或附近區域撚狗<br />\n每次撚狗斬喺遊行附近撚<br />\n你叫勇武點出來？<br />\n班狗出得不反對通知書<br />\n代表既係佢對示威區域或附近有一系列措施去應對「開花」<br />\n明唔明？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全力以赴<br />\n光復香港</span>"},{"pid":"ee6af6f204b04ea7546ae8b59fc61474250aa033","tid":1768061,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:30:05.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"d5e9bedd8010cf21f12617a30fb7699170322017","tid":1768061,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:30:14.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"c59562b94bb92553fb633720d39d2a5ce7782466","tid":1768061,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee6af6f204b04ea7546ae8b59fc61474250aa033","tid":1768061,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:30:05.000Z","msg":"p"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:31:50.000Z","msg":"Thank you<br />\n<br />\n可以分享喺tg谷如果你覺得我有道理<br />\n<br />\n有野補充或修改都可以同我講返"},{"pid":"9167923b4030e3a2f9d80d5ff1941320581033e8","tid":1768061,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T20:33:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ccb721019b03dd416979051f1a9f3609f8ffe61","tid":1768061,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike